spec_data.Name: perl-CGI-Compile
spec_data.Description:
CGI::Compile is an utility to compile CGI scripts into a code reference
that can run many times on its own namespace, as long as the script is
ready to run on a persistent environment.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:02:01 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Compile .cgi scripts to a code reference like ModPerl::Registry
